          <title>
            <string language="en">Behaviour of phospholipids in water</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Verhalten der Phospholipide im Wasser</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Comportement des phospholipides dans l'eau</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Comportamento dos phospholipids na água</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Comportamento dei fosfolipidi in acqua</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Συμπεριφορά των φωσφολιπιδίων στο ύδωρ</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Comportamiento de phospholipids en agua</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the behaviour of phospholipids in water. The hydrophilic heads line up along the water while the hydrophobic tails project out of the water.</string>
          </description>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">hydrophilic head</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">hydrophobic tail</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">phospholipids</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <structure>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt das Verhalten der 
Phospholipide im Wasser. Die hydrophilen Köpfe richten entlang 
dem Wasser aus, während die hydrophoben Endstücke aus dem Wasser 
heraus sich projizieren.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre le comportement des 
phospholipides dans l'eau. Les chefs hydrophiles alignent le 
long de l'eau tandis que les queues hydrophobes projettent hors de 
l'eau.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra o comportamento dos 
phospholipids na água. A linha de cabeças hydrophilic acima ao
longo da água quando as caudas hydrophobic se projetarem fora da 
água.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra il comportamento dei 
fosfolipidi in acqua. Le teste idrofile allineano lungo l'acqua 
mentre le code idrofobe si proiettano dall'acqua.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει τη συμπεριφορά των 
φωσφολιπιδίων στο ύδωρ. Τα υδρόφιλα κεφάλια παρατάσσουν 
κατά μήκος του ύδατος ενώ το υδροφοβικό πρόγραμμα ουρών από το
ύδωρ.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra el comportamiento de 
phospholipids en agua. Las pistas hidrofílicas se alinean a lo 
largo del agua mientras que las colas hidrofóbicas proyectan fuera 
del agua.</string>
          </description>
